Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:05.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:08.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Got a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.61,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to talk to me \Ntoo much at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:16.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I want the drug that\Nmakes me normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.90,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:25.76,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Before school started, you asked once,\Nso you could formally quit your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:28.15,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What's it for this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:32.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to visit a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've done your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You know about my senpai\N at that company, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.79,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...is the anniversary of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:19.53,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}A Trip to the Past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.63,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go looking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:22.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And risk running into someone else \Nwho worked with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not that any of them will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.70,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.41,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.06,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.91,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.48,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I know you need to keep an eye on me,\Nso just do it from a distance like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No need to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:43.76,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We were watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:48.89,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We know you froze up \Nat Saiki-san's grave last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We're worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.52,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Worried you might impulsively follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:03:00.16,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Or not be able to control yourself \Nif a coworker shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.95,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.24,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.14,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.61,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would go pale if\Nsomeone tried to strangle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.68,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't apply that much pressure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:34.11,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But you're doing better than you were \Nright after you resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.98,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even tighten a necktie then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.68,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.96,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:46.37,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You can visit the grave, and I'll get you\Nthe medicine, but only if I can come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want, you sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.62,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I appreciate the compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:53.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.01,sign_5878_48_Trauma_from_the_,,0000,0000,0082,,Trauma from the suicide \Nof the senpai he'd trained under
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.14,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.51,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.33,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Writing a medicine request for\NKaizaki-san and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.38,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.49,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to visit her grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.99,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,If memory serves, it's dangerous\N for him to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.05,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:36.11,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, they'll only approve it \Nfor the assigned support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:40.84,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I could totally go like this, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Two grown men and a high school girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.94,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks. I don't want\Nthe police questioning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.47,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But sorry, Onoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.23,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.46,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know it was a suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.77,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Memorial service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.16,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have pried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:19.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often that you start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.04,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:23.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.72,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:31.12,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The change is done in about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.91,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:36.42,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Should we spend the hour together, \Nfighting off the drowsiness side effect?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We can just nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:42.31,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:46.09,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san, you wake up well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You even look into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.85,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.35,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, I'm the type \Nto sleep through alarms,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.98,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so wake me up if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:01.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What? You sleep through alarms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do every morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:07.74,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If I have somewhere to be, I sleep sitting up \Nso that I don't sleep that deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like a samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,How do you ever feel rested?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:15.31,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've gotta do your job \Non top of going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.00,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.79,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We've really grown close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.97,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're even worrying about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You should really get a girlfriend \Nwho'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe An?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:29.88,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.44,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I feel tired just thinking about \Nher waking me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she wakes up hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.75,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,See you in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.66,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.70,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sleepy, my foot! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.66,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to wake you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Waking you up is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:30.67,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four months since \Nwe met each other as adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.01,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.70,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Kaizaki Arata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.57,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Time sure flies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,A third of the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.41,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just look sad because you were \Nimagining this experiment ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:54.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm only in this for a year's \Nliving expenses and a job introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.92,sign_11561_121_An_Onoya,,0000,0000,0000,,Onoya An
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.92,sign_11561_121_It_s_okay_,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.32,sign_11646_122_It_s_okay_,,0001,0126,0149,,{\fad(1,500)}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.32,sign_11652_123_Got_it__Thanks_,,0108,0001,0065,,{\fad(1,500)}Got it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.89,sign_11875_125_Saiki,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.50,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.75,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We've been here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:25.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:33.01,sign_12181_130_Talking,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:33.01,sign_12194_131_to,,0000,0000,0000,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:29.55,sign_12205_132____,,0000,0000,0000,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:33.01,sign_12217_133____Senpai,,0000,0000,0000,,...Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.31,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.99,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you tactless bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.99,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.76,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we get lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:51.86,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,This was your first big sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.39,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Let me, Michiru-senpai, treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was a new hire, and she was my trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.00,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She had the best sales \Nrecord of any employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.12,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,At first I was surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:05.42,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,to be working under a woman in sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.55,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But Saiki Michiru-senpai was super friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:16.32,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Daily overtime, hard work,\N and wages that in no way justified it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The mood was always tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.32,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The job I'd struggled to find
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.15,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,was at one of those black companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.25,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Running out of steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.33,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together, Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.45,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yet Senpai still visibly enjoyed her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.03,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She was strong and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.83,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I admired her, and she kept me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.44,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.30,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.87,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must've sabotaged you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:56.82,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people don't like me\Njust because I'm a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.86,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:01.99,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't say anything, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:07.14,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, \Nand I'm glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:10.00,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:12.64,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.57,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.01,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kaizaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.76,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,...grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.34,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.37,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.63,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't she quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.28,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off. The new guy's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:32.91,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. She's in charge of his training, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:35.91,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rat us out, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.58,0:10:39.41,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.15,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're grown men. Have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.60,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I ignored what she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.06,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,acted on my own sense of justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and wasted all her efforts to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.40,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the harassment got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.51,Flashback Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.37,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought she was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.94,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But she was not "fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.20,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,The cops closed their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:27.95,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,They've concluded it was suicide. \NNo signs of foul play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.21,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you keep this confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:32.29,Flashback Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.17,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.30,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't butted in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.30,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:41.59,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Who d'ya think'll get \Npromoted instead of Saiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.01,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno... maybe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.72,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.06,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're already doing this now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:52.19,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Saiki was very proud of our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.44,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's why she chose \Nto end things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.57,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,She just loved this place that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:02.53,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I hold her much beloved company\Nas my pride and joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.95,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Well, get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.41,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.37,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.62,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is {\i1}wrong{\i0} with you all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.79,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just died here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.29,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel anything at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.42,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,How can you act like nothing happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.68,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that\Nmaybe it was your fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.68,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.18,Flashback Dialogue,Coworker,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it out on the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.22,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.39,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.50,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,After only three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.04,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Society will think you're gutless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.55,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,That fact'll be on your resume forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.01,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think anyone else will hire you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:08.39,sign_18798_218_Resignation,,0000,0000,0000,,Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.80,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.39,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forget this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.39,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.19,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid to go job-hunting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.56,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But that's better than...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.53,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...spending another second\Nin this rotten company!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.41,sign_19326_226_Resignation,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.70,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.95,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Only upper-level management\N gets to "resign."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.12,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Scrubs like you "give notice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.84,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You went to grad school,\N and you don't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.59,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,We won't even notice you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.38,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Get out right this instant,\N you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.05,Flashback Dialogue,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, and don't ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.60,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.64,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:58.52,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I grew afraid to engage with\N people and society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.78,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been more grown-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd killed my emotions\N and tried to fit in,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,could I have remained a\Nproductive member of society?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.79,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Would that have been better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.33,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was lost in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.67,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.63,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Coming here just fills me with regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.25,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.77,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.12,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We're from the same company, \Nhired a year after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.08,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen your face in a company album.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.83,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,And the old hires talk about you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.91,Main Dialogue,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Kamioka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.54,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.50,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:07.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet that place \Nis still griping about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.55,Main Dialogue,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:14.26,Main Dialogue,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Boss still loves to bring up the story of\Nthe guy who quit after only three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:18.52,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,He talks about Saiki-senpai \Nlike a fallen warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:21.98,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,"She loved this company!\N You should follow her example."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.69,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We'd just graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.65,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We had no idea what\Na normal workplace was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.28,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even know if we were\Nworking for a black company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:37.08,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We'd love to quit, but we're afraid\N everywhere is like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.79,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,so we just grumble and keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.92,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They look half-dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.92,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like they're desperately hanging on to\Na thread that might snap at any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.76,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm looking at\Nmyself from a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.68,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,So it's an honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.55,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,You're practically our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Giving that president \Na piece of your mind and walking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:01.81,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.15,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a dumb kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No patience, ruled by emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.23,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.78,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the courage to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:13.36,Main Dialogue,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone can do what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.70,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea what a help it's been to know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.75,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,we weren't the only ones who thought \Nour company was messed-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.04,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We really admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.59,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,And Saiki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.71,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought my rebellion\Nwould have such an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.13,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.80,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,has it been hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.43,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,After leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Just... it would help to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:54.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,After I quit,\NI couldn't do anything for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.95,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to work to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:17:00.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I started looking for another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,The day of my first interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I realized I couldn't wear a necktie anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,When they asked me why I quit \Nafter three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find the words to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:15.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,In time, I regained my ability\Nto get through interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,but I never did get hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then I got sick and tired of it all, gave up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and got a job at a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.48,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,You still work there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.03,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Saiki,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together, Kaizaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still doing part-time work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:42.58,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda hard to face\Nmy friends with real jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.16,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but that's reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.17,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not selfless enough to give my one \Nand only life to that shitty company!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hindsight is 20/20 and all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,but there are people I've met because I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world I would never have\N experienced if I'd stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.03,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.99,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence gives strength to\Nthe people who came after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.12,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:32.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That the new hires saw me in that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:36.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You arranged things so we'd \Nbump into each other there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.18,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.55,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That was pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:44.26,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But why'd you lie and say you were \Nstill doing part-time work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.52,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You have a real job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:52.52,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're a test subject, and you're getting\Npaid enough to make ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.69,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd call that a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:58.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but it's not a job I found myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I really did struggle after I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.16,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And I wound up here because \NI didn't find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:09.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be irresponsible to tell them \NI'd found a real job again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:15.25,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pretend you have work \Nin front of your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.63,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,but tell your juniors the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.93,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you're a hero to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me. I'll get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:25.89,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:34.61,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Onoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.61,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:40.99,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be with Kaizaki-san the whole day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.87,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so keep me updated on \Nwhat these two are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.08,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,New hires this year \Nat Kaizaki-san's old company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.75,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,They've visited Saiki-san's grave\Nseveral times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.46,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they might go on\Nthe anniversary of her death, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:02.93,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If he learns that what he did gives hope\Nto those that came after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:06.76,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,it might help him start looking forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.64,Flashback Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.98,Flashback Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,You dug that deep for Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.02,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the Support Division's\N supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:18.86,Flashback Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,But won't they say you're \Ngetting too involved again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.65,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just bringing them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.49,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to Kaizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.54,sign_29445_353_How_d_Kaizaki_sa,An,0000,0000,0000,,How'd Kaizaki-san do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.42,sign_29445_353_How_d_Kaizaki_sa,An,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him talking to the new hires
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:35.21,sign_29445_353_How_d_Kaizaki_sa,An,0000,0000,0000,,but couldn't hear what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.25,sign_29445_353_How_d_Kaizaki_sa,An,0000,0000,0000,,What were they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.80,sign_29445_353_How_d_Kaizaki_sa,An,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Senpai!\NI can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.55,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.34,sign_29787_363_Mm__I_think_he_s,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think he's\N feeling better. \NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.09,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:47.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I talked to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that my voice and Senpai's\N reached someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.57,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't erase the guilt \NI feel for not saving her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,but it helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:07.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I went there, I'd always\Nend up regretting everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:12.99,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure she was watching with a face\Nthat screamed, "Get a hold of yourself!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I could finally tell her I was glad I'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If not for ReLIFE...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:23.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been alone, \NI couldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.18,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was stand there and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Just say, "You're welcome!" Yeesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.94,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I should say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.19,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:47.07,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Now who won't say, "You're welcome"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:39.93,Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still taking make-ups, Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.03,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.42,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that! Help me, Oga-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-kun! Showga!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:37.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break's almost here—\Nwait, what's with that nickname?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:39.93,Next Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1)}Double Panic
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.44,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, summer vacation!
